{"tid":565155,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾發表中國滲透政界研究　紐西蘭學者近日辦公室、家居被爆竊　收警告信","createTime":"2018-02-18T17:05:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T02:26:44.000Z","uid":53379,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5b6beae31b4ed87c288913a8de0e304d436d465a","tid":565155,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T17:05:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">曾發表中國滲透政界研究　紐西蘭學者近日辦公室、家居被爆竊　收警告信<br />\n<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/brady_ZCOzL_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fbrady_ZCOzL_1200x0.png&h=dbc83430&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名曾發表論文研究中國如何在外國建立政治影響力的紐西蘭學者，周五向澳洲國會透露，近日其辦公室及家居接連被闖入爆竊，她又收到指她將受到襲擊的警告信，她在中國時訪問的消息來源亦被中國當局問話。<br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭坎特伯雷大學（University of Canterbury）教授Anne-Marie Brady，周五在澳洲國會的情報及安全委員會作證時透露，近日發生三宗令她憂慮的事件，包括去年12月其辦公室被爆竊、本周收到她將會被襲擊的警告信，而昨日其家居亦被爆竊。<br />\n<br />\n她指，家居被爆竊的事件最可疑，因為3部可攜式電腦及電話均被偷，但其他值錢的財物卻完好無缺，警方正調查事件。<br />\n<br />\nBrady又透露，自從她發報有關中國南極政策的研究後，其大學僱主亦被施壓，而她在中國訪問時的消息來源，均被中國國安問話。<br />\n<br />\nBrady去年9月刊出一份論文《魔術武器（Magic Weapons）》，以紐西蘭為案例，研究中國如何在國外施加影響力，引起國內外廣泛關注，論文提到執政黨收到大筆政治捐獻，與及一些前高官及現任高官的家屬如何獲委入中國國營銀行、企業及智庫的董事局內。<br />\n<br />\n該研究引發新西蘭優先黨提出要作出調查，而澳洲現時正引入法例遏止中國在當地政治的影響。<br />\n<br />\nBrady又提到，中國的非國家活動，正以統一陣線（united front)的名號下被協調統調，以左右公眾輿論及政治精英，去支持其冒起的新外交政策。<br />\n<br />\n「澳洲及紐西蘭似乎是近年這一策略的試驗區，而現時已去到關鍵水平。」她表示。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/曾發表中國滲透政界研究-紐西蘭學者近日辦公室-家居被爆竊-收警告信/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%9B%BE%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%BB%B2%E9%80%8F%E6%94%BF%E7%95%8C%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6-%E7%B4%90%E8%A5%BF%E8%98%AD%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85%E8%BF%91%E6%97%A5%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%A4-%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%85%E8%A2%AB%E7%88%86%E7%AB%8A-%E6%94%B6%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E4%BF%A1%2F&d=2bcU3BXsMNDy0vb8v51sIOI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=0c895ba7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%9B%BE%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%BB%B2%E9%80%8F%E6%94%BF%E7%95%8C%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6-%E7%B4%90%E8%A5%BF%E8%98%AD%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85%E8%BF%91%E6%97%A5%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%A4-%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%85%E8%A2%AB%E7%88%86%E7%AB%8A-%E6%94%B6%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E4%BF%A1%2F&h=1260b2b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/曾發表中國滲透政界研究-紐西蘭學者近日辦公室-家居被爆竊-收警告信/</a>"},{"pid":"0be722705a88a4694e9c2c55827d2d42a3b4685d","tid":565155,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T01:30:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"763aeabbab61116408b883e0ee2fdf83075476d0","tid":565155,"uid":38523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T01:31:54.000Z","msg":"支狗係咪冇腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係人都知邊個做啦"},{"pid":"ea2b5d633c850252378ddcb0e0d38f3f418d92d2","tid":565155,"uid":27038,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T01:43:12.000Z","msg":"屌你，中國=有錢版北韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c697d9afa314d701fd302cd77998aee370ecbd79","tid":565155,"uid":37735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T02:04:42.000Z","msg":"聯手抵抗支那侵略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b582220d4db26cb991f5f7d8bf82f4a483d8438","tid":565155,"uid":37735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T02:05:42.000Z","msg":"西式開放民主<br />\n<br />\n被支那，俄羅斯同一堆國家利用<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb3e124a6722500cec7b60a34c1f3f5664bbab3","tid":565155,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b582220d4db26cb991f5f7d8bf82f4a483d8438","tid":565155,"uid":37735,"